    I'm an Associate Professor of Philosophy at [NYU Shanghai][nyush], Global Network Professor of [Philosophy][nyu-phil] at [New York University][nyu], and a Guest Professor of Philosophy at [East China Normal University][ecnu].  I work in philosophy of science, especially causation and explanation, and on related topics in philosophy of physics, philosophy of biology and philosophy of mind.
    
    #### selected publications
    - “[Exclusion Excluded](https://philpapers.org/archive/wesee.pdf)”, in Alastair Wilson and Katie Robertson (Eds), *Levels of Explanation*, Oxford, 2024, pp. 101–135.
    - “[Difference-Making, Closure and Exclusion](https://philpapers.org/archive/wesdca-3.pdf)”, in Helen Beebee, Chris Hitchcock and Huw Price (Eds), *Making a Difference: Essays on the Philosophy of Causation*, Oxford, 2017, pp. 215–231.
    - “[Statistical Mechanical Imperialism](http://philpapers.org/archive/wessmi.pdf)”, in Alastair Wilson (Ed), *Chance and Temporal Asymmetry*, Oxford, 2014, pp. 241–257.
    - “[Proportionality, Contrast and Explanation](http://philpapers.org/archive/wespca-2.pdf)”, in *Australasian Journal of Philosophy*, <span class="sc">vol</span>. 91, <span class="sc">no</span>. 4, 2013, pp. 785–797.
    - “[Explanatory Depth](http://philpapers.org/archive/wesed.pdf)”, in *Philosophy of Science*, <span class="sc">vol</span>. 77, <span class="sc">no</span>. 2, <span class="sc">apr</span> 2010, pp. 273–294.
    - “[The Time-Asymmetry of Causation](http://philpapers.org/archive/pritto.pdf)” (with [Huw Price][huw]), in Helen Beebee, Chris Hitchcock and Peter Menzies (Eds), *The Oxford Handbook of Causation*, Oxford, Oxford, 2009, pp. 414–443.

